<sect2 id="Borderlayout"><title>Borderlayout</title>
<para>The layout component is a nested component. The parent component is <code>borderlayout</code>, and its children components include north, south, center, west, and east. The combination of children components of <code>borderlayout</code> is free.</para>
<para>
<graphic fileref="images/layout.jpg"/>
</para>
<programlisting>&lt;borderlayout height="500px"&gt;&#13;    &lt;north size="50%" border="0"&gt;&#13;        &lt;borderlayout&gt;&#13;            &lt;west size="25%" border="none" flex="true"&gt;&#13;                &lt;div style="background:#B8D335"&gt;&#13;                    &lt;label value="25%"&#13;                        style="color:white;font-size:50px" /&gt;&#13;                &lt;/div&gt;&#13;            &lt;/west&gt;&#13;            &lt;center border="none" flex="true"&gt;&#13;                &lt;div style="background:#E6D92C"&gt;&#13;                    &lt;label value="25%"&#13;                        style="color:white;font-size:50px" /&gt;&#13;                &lt;/div&gt;&#13;            &lt;/center&gt;&#13;            &lt;east size="50%" border="none" flex="true"&gt;&#13;                &lt;label value="Here is a non-border"&#13;                    style="color:gray;font-size:30px" /&gt;&#13;            &lt;/east&gt;&#13;        &lt;/borderlayout&gt;&#13;    &lt;/north&gt;&#13;    &lt;center border="0"&gt;&#13;        &lt;borderlayout&gt;&#13;            &lt;west size="30%" flex="true" border="0"&gt;&#13;                &lt;div style="background:#E6D92C"&gt;&#13;                    &lt;label value="30%"&#13;                        style="color:white;font-size:50px" /&gt;&#13;                &lt;/div&gt;&#13;            &lt;/west&gt;&#13;            &lt;center&gt;&#13;                &lt;label value="Here is a border"&#13;                    style="color:gray;font-size:30px" /&gt;&#13;            &lt;/center&gt;&#13;            &lt;east size="30%" flex="true" border="0"&gt;&#13;                &lt;div style="background:#B8D335"&gt;&#13;                    &lt;label value="30%"&#13;                        style="color:white;font-size:50px" /&gt;&#13;                &lt;/div&gt;&#13;            &lt;/east&gt;&#13;        &lt;/borderlayout&gt;&#13;    &lt;/center&gt;&#13;&lt;/borderlayout&gt;&#13;</programlisting><sect3><title>Class Name</title>
